Name: Device_Type
Description: Type of the logical device and its functionality

Name: Sync_Comm_Period
Description: us period defines the SYNC interval

Name: Sync_Window
Description: us length of the time window for synchronous PDOs

Name: Mfg_Device_Name
Description: name of the device as given by the manufacturer

Name: Guard_Time
Description: configured guard time respectively the life time factor

Name: Life_Time_Factor
Description: life time factor multiplied with the guard time gives the life time for the life guarding protocol

Name: Store_Param
Description: restore default parameters- highest sub-index supported

Name: EMCY_COB_Id
Description: COB-ID for the EMCY write service

Name: EMCY_Inhibit
Description: inhibit time for the EMCY message

Name: Consumer_Heartbeat_time
Description: indicate the expected heartbeat cycle times - Highest sub-index supported

Name: Producer_Heartbeat_Time
Description: producer heartbeat time shall indicate the configured cycle time of the heartbeat
